OL,3,CMan who posted racist messages about
OL,4,CEngland player Jess Carter spared jail
OL,6,FA 60-year-old man who posted racist
OL,7,Fmessages about England footballer Jess
OL,8,FCarter online has received a suspended
OL,9,Fjail sentence.
OL,11,FNigel Dewale, of Great Harwood,
OL,12,FLancashire, sent two posts during the
OL,13,FUEFA Women's EURO 2025 tournament last
OL,14,Fsummer from his TikTok account under
OL,15,Fthe username Bogeyman.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
