OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774515911
OL,3,CMan who posted racist messages about
OL,4,CEngland player Jess Carter spared jail
OL,6,FDewale was "in drink" at home when he
OL,7,Fresponded to a news article about
OL,8,Fpolice investigating online racial
OL,9,Fabuse earlier received by Carter
OL,10,Ffollowing England's ties against
OL,11,FFrance and Sweden at the championships.
OL,13,FAs well as racially offensive slurs,
OL,14,Fhe wrote: "Women's football is
OL,15,Fdiabolical. Should not be on national
OL,16,FTV."
OL,18,FThe messages were later traced to
OL,19,FDewale who was arrested and charged.
OL,26,@nD@LOUnD@UO]vD@KOU
