OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774515911
OL,3,CMan who posted racist messages about
OL,4,CEngland player Jess Carter spared jail
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, he was sentenced at
OL,7,FBlackburn Magistrates' Court to six
OL,8,Fweeks in custody, suspended for 12
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FHe pleaded guilty at an earlier
OL,12,Fhearing to sending a grossly offensive
OL,13,Fmessage via a public communications
OL,14,Fnetwork.
OL,16,FCarter, 28, who is from Warwick and
OL,17,Fplays for US team Gotham FC, was part
OL,18,Fof the Lionesses squad that went on to
OL,19,Fsuccessfully defend their title at the
OL,20,Ftournament in Switzerland.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
